<div class="main topBox floatLeft">        <div class="topTitleBox warau"><div class="top-Ttl_Wrap">                <h2 class="top-Ttl_Img-warau"><img src="https://gamepark.akamaized.net/warau.gamepark.net/images/top/h2_title20200626.svg" alt="GamePark" width="580"><a href="/c/AGKNWQgZdqObkPIFBWhemw"><img class="displayBlock" style="position: absolute; top: 20px; left: 600px; z-index: 2;" src="https://gamepark.akamaized.net/warau.gamepark.net/images/top/san.png" alt=" "></a><div class="ttl4 marginLeft5">毎日遊べる！メダルを貯めてポイントGETしよう</div></h2><!--  -->                                        <p class="displayNone">毎日ゲームで遊んでメダルを貯めよう</p><a href="/play/select/" class="linkBlk">		<div class="topAbout171023">        <div class="bln"><span class="ttl3">ゲーム1回<br />につき2枚</span></div><ul class="clearfix">				<li class="partic">					<span class="top-About3step_topText ttlBlk">1,ゲームで遊んで<br>参加賞メダルGET</span>                					<div class="btmTxtBox ttl5"><div class="btmTxt">全員に参加賞<br /><span class="ttl1">毎日最大</span><span class="scr">260枚</span></div>					</div>				</li>				<li class="rank">					<span class="top-About3step_topText ttlBlk">2,ゲーム得点を競って<br />入賞メダルGET</span>					<img class="top-Step2_Inner" height="100" src="https://gamepark.akamaized.net/static.gamepark.net/images/common/icon_medal.svg" alt="" height="122">					<div class="btmTxtBox ttl5"><div class="btmTxt">ゲーム大会で<br /><span class="ttl1">毎日最大</span><span class="scr">130枚</span></div></div>				</li>				<li class="exchange top-Step3_Wrap">					<span class="top-About3step_topText ttlBlk">3,メダル100枚で抽選<br>ポイントGET</span>					<div class="top-Step3_Inner"><img class="top-Step3_Inner-imgLeft" height="80" src="https://gamepark.akamaized.net/static.gamepark.net/images/top/icon_lottery.svg" alt=""><img class="top-Step3_Inner-imgRight" height="80" src="https://cf.gamepark.net/warau-plus.gamepark.net/images/medal/obj_exc_pt.png" alt=" "></div>					<div class="btmTxtBox ttl5"><div class="btmTxt">1等が当たると<br /><span class="scr">2,000</span><span class="ttl1 scr">ポイント</span></div></div>				</li>			</ul></div></a>	<div class="btBox">        <div class="btBase btFull btGrn"><a href="https://www.warau.jp/"><span>ゲームで遊んでメダルを貯める</span></a></div></div>    </div></div>        <div class="sw-AdNetWorkDouble"><div class="sw-AdNetWork_Banner-336"><!-- 250_Lrectangle_2 -->
